      • hasCompletedWithError

        public boolean hasCompletedWithError()
        Description copied from interface: ISSRFuture
        Indicates whether the execution of the SSR exited with an exception.

        Please not that if SSR could not be sent or run into a timeout without getting any answer from Sunrise RT, this method will return false. Please use ISSRFuture.isCompleted() to check whether a reply for this SSR was received.

        Specified by:
        hasCompletedWithError in interface ISSRFuture
        Returns:
        true, if the SSR execution was erroneous
        false, if the SSR was executed successfully or hasn't completed yet
